TRMh","''",[59,825,550],{"class":101},[59,827,829,831,833,835],{"class":61,"line":828},43,[59,830,817],{"class":540},[59,832,544],{"class":101},[59,834,744],{"class":540},[59,836,550],{"class":101},[59,838,840],{"class":61,"line":839},44,[59,841,623],{"class":101},[59,843,845,847],{"class":61,"line":844},45,[59,846,40],{"class":97},[59,848,534],{"class":101},[59,850,852,855,857,860],{"class":61,"line":851},46,[59,853,854],{"class":540},"  border-collapse",[59,856,544],{"class":101},[59,858,859],{"class":540},"collapse",[59,861,550],{"class":101},[59,863,865,868,870,872],{"class":61,"line":864},47,[59,866,867],{"class":540},"  border-spacing",[59,869,544],{"class":101},[59,871,547],{"class":540},[59,873,550],{"class":101},[59,875,877],{"class":61,"line":876},48,[59,878,623],{"class":101},[16,880,881,882,885],{},"通常上面這一段 Reset CSS 會放在我們自己撰寫的 CSS 之前，也就是一開始，盡可能在執行 CSS 樣式表之前就先清空 HTML 全部樣式，注意是",[277,883,884],{},"全部樣式","。",[16,887,888],{},"而 Eric A. Meyer 作者自已本身也常常被各家瀏覽器的預設樣式不同所困擾，甚至特別強調過 IE 真的很雷",[171,890,891],{},[16,892,893],{},"The maddening barrier to this is, yes, Internet Explorer.",[16,895,896],{},"雖然時至今日 IE 已經功成身退，而各家瀏覽器的預設樣式也越來越統一，可是還是有機會遇到不統一的問題，畢竟每一個瀏覽器更新的版本都不同，因此對於 W3C 制訂的支援程度也就會跟著不同。",[16,898,899],{},"而我們也可以發現 2.0 的版本最後更新於 2011 年距離至今也十年了，所以代表著 HTML5 很早就已經開始實作，但是開始大量使用也只不過是近期的事情而已。",[16,901,902],{},"而 Reset CSS 並沒有使用到過度難以理解的語法，主要是這些：",[348,904,905,911,917,923,929,935,941,947,953,959,965,971,976,982],{},[353,906,907,910],{},[38,908,909],{},"margin: 0;"," - 外邊界",[353,912,913,916],{},[38,914,915],{},"padding: 0;"," - 內邊界",[353,918,919,922],{},[38,920,921],{},"border: 0;"," - 線條",[353,924,925,928],{},[38,926,927],{},"font-size: 100%;"," - 字體大小",[353,930,931,934],{},[38,932,933],{},"font: inherit;"," - 字型風格",[353,936,937,940],{},[38,938,939],{},"vertical-align: baseline;"," - 垂直方向",[353,942,943,946],{},[38,944,945],{},"display: block;"," - 顯示類型",[353,948,949,952],{},[38,950,951],{},"line-height: 1;"," -  間距",[353,954,955,958],{},[38,956,957],{},"list-style: none;"," - 列表樣式",[353,960,961,964],{},[38,962,963],{},"quotes: none;"," - 引號樣式",[353,966,967,970],{},[38,968,969],{},"content: '';"," - 內容（通常用於偽元素）",[353,972,973,970],{},[38,974,975],{},"content: none;",[353,977,978,981],{},[38,979,980],{},"border-collapse: collapse;"," - 邊框分開或合併的設置",[353,983,984,987],{},[38,985,986],{},"border-spacing: 0;"," - 邊框的距離",[16,989,990,991,994,995,997,998,1000,1001,1003,1004,1006],{},"可以看到這邊比較特別的是常用於偽元素的 ",[38,992,993],{},"content"," 寫了兩次，主要原因是當時的瀏覽器大多都只支援 ",[38,996,744],{}," 的屬性，但是當時 Safari 與 Chrome 卻只支援 ",[38,999,823],{}," 方式，因此假使 ",[38,1002,975],{},"不被支援的時候，就會改走 ",[38,1005,969],{}," 這樣才能夠確保瀏覽器樣式樣式的統一性。",[12,1008,1010],{"id":1009},"normalizecss","Normalize.css",[16,1012,1013],{},"Normalize.css 也是一種 Reset CSS，但是它與 meyerweb CSS 最大差異在於它保留了瀏覽器預設的樣式，而它的特色有以下：",[348,1015,1016,1019,1022],{},[353,1017,1018],{},"保留預設樣式(也支援 HTML5)",[353,1020,1021],{},"修正瀏覽器本身的 Bug",[353,1023,1024],{},"清楚的註解",[16,1026,1027,1028,1032],{},"那麼因為 ",[27,1029,1010],{"href":1030,"rel":1031},"https:\u002F\u002Fnecolas.github.io\u002Fnormalize.css\u002F",[31]," 內容較多，因此建議直接到它的官方網站觀看。",[147,1034,1035],{"id":1035},"保留預設樣式",[16,1037,1038,1039,1042,1043,1045],{},"在 meyerweb 版本我們可以看到 ",[38,1040,1041],{},"h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6,"," 樣式都是被清空清除的，那麼 Normalize.css 則是選擇保留這些預設樣式，這也代表著你不用針對 ",[38,1044,1041],{}," 標籤重新給予樣式。",[16,1047,1048,1049,1051],{},"那麼為什麼他們敢這樣子做呢？因為 Normalize.css 作者花了數百小時去了解各家瀏覽器的默認樣式差異，然後再去做調整，除非有特定瀏覽器的預設樣式改變了才會去額外調整，否則基本上會盡可能去保留原始的瀏覽器樣式，舉例來講 ",[38,1050,138],{}," 標籤在各家瀏覽器上就有稍微不同：",[50,1053,1055],{"className":52,"code":1054,"language":54,"meta":55,"style":55},"\u002F**\n * Correct the font size and margin on `h1` elements within `section` and\n * `article` contexts in Chrome, Firefox, and Safari.\n *\u002F\n\nh1 {\n  font-size: 2em;\n  margin: 0.67em 0;\n}\n",[38,1056,1057,1062,1067,1072,1077,1081,1087,1100,1116],{"__ignoreMap":55},[59,1058,1059],{"class":61,"line":62},[59,1060,1061],{"class":65},"\u002F**\n",[59,1063,1064],{"class":61,"line":69},[59,1065,1066],{"class":65}," * Correct the font size and margin on `h1` elements within `section` and\n",[59,1068,1069],{"class":61,"line":75},[59,1070,1071],{"class":65}," * `article` contexts in Chrome, Firefox, and Safari.\n",[59,1073,1074],{"class":61,"line":81},[59,1075,1076],{"class":65}," *\u002F\n",[59,1078,1079],{"class":61,"line":87},[59,1080,91],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":90},[59,1082,1083,1085],{"class":61,"line":94},[59,1084,138],{"class":97},[59,1086,534],{"class":101},[59,1088,1089,1091,1093,1096,1098],{"class":61,"line":135},[59,1090,580],{"class":540},[59,1092,544],{"class":101},[59,1094,1095],{"class":540},"2",[59,1097,229],{"class":588},[59,1099,550],{"class":101},[59,1101,1102,1104,1106,1109,1111,1114],{"class":61,"line":180},[59,1103,541],{"class":540},[59,1105,544],{"class":101},[59,1107,1108],{"class":540},"0.67",[59,1110,229],{"class":588},[59,1112,1113],{"class":540}," 0",[59,1115,550],{"class":101},[59,1117,1118],{"class":61,"line":216},[59,1119,623],{"class":101},[16,1121,1122,1123,1125],{},"基本上唯獨可以比較明顯的發現每一個瀏覽器的 ",[38,1124,105],{}," 間距都是不同的：",[50,1127,1129],{"className":52,"code":1128,"language":54,"meta":55,"style":55},"\u002F**\n * Remove the margin in all browsers.\n *\u002F\n\nbody {\n  margin: 0;\n}\n",[38,1130,1131,1135,1140,1144,1148,1154,1164],{"__ignoreMap":55},[59,1132,1133],{"class":61,"line":62},[59,1134,1061],{"class":65},[59,1136,1137],{"class":61,"line":69},[59,1138,1139],{"class":65}," * Remove the margin in all browsers.\n",[59,1141,1142],{"class":61,"line":75},[59,1143,1076],{"class":65},[59,1145,1146],{"class":61,"line":81},[59,1147,91],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":90},[59,1149,1150,1152],{"class":61,"line":87},[59,1151,105],{"class":97},[59,1153,534],{"class":101},[59,1155,1156,1158,1160,1162],{"class":61,"line":94},[59,1157,541],{"class":540},[59,1159,544],{"class":101},[59,1161,547],{"class":540},[59,1163,550],{"class":101},[59,1165,1166],{"class":61,"line":135},[59,1167,623],{"class":101},[147,1169,1021],{"id":1170},"修正瀏覽器本身的-bug",[16,1172,1173],{},"這一個算是滿好玩的設置，舉例來講在 iOS 和 Safari 中會有無法設置點擊的樣式問題：",[50,1175,1177],{"className":52,"code":1176,"language":54,"meta":55,"style":55},"\u002F**\n * Correct the inability to style clickable types in iOS and Safari.\n *\u002F\n\nbutton,\n[type=\"button\"],\n[type=\"reset\"],\n[type=\"submit\"] {\n  -webkit-appearance: button;\n}\n",[38,1178,1179,1183,1188,1192,1196,1203,1220,1233,1247,1255],{"__ignoreMap":55},[59,1180,1181],{"class":61,"line":62},[59,1182,1061],{"class":65},[59,1184,1185],{"class":61,"line":69},[59,1186,1187],{"class":65}," * Correct the inability to style clickable types in iOS and Safari.\n",[59,1189,1190],{"class":61,"line":75},[59,1191,1076],{"class":65},[59,1193,1194],{"class":61,"line":81},[59,1195,91],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":90},[59,1197,1198,1201],{"class":61,"line":87},[59,1199,1200],{"class":97},"button",[59,1202,132],{"class":101},[59,1204,1205,1208,1211,1214,1217],{"class":61,"line":94},[59,1206,1207],{"class":101},"[",[59,1209,1210],{"class":540},"type",[59,1212,1213],{"class":588},"=",[59,1215,1216],{"class":822},"\"button\"",[59,1218,1219],{"class":101},"],\n",[59,1221,1222,1224,1226,1228,1231],{"class":61,"line":135},[59,1223,1207],{"class":101},[59,1225,1210],{"class":540},[59,1227,1213],{"class":588},[59,1229,1230],{"class":822},"\"reset\"",[59,1232,1219],{"class":101},[59,1234,1235,1237,1239,1241,1244],{"class":61,"line":180},[59,1236,1207],{"class":101},[59,1238,1210],{"class":540},[59,1240,1213],{"class":588},[59,1242,1243],{"class":822},"\"submit\"",[59,1245,1246],{"class":101},"] {\n",[59,1248,1249,1252],{"class":61,"line":216},[59,1250,1251],{"class":540},"  -webkit-appearance",[59,1253,1254],{"class":101},": button;\n",[59,1256,1257],{"class":61,"line":264},[59,1258,623],{"class":101},[147,1260,1024],{"id":1024},[16,1262,1263],{},"這是另一個我個人滿喜歡 Normalize.css 的地方，每一行的設置它都會清楚說明這是在做什麼，畢竟如果有寫清楚的話，我們也可以知道為什麼它這樣子做(這邊就不示範了，前面範例都有一推註解)。",[16,1265,1266,1267,1272],{},"而它官方 GitHub 也都有詳細的 ",[27,1268,1271],{"href":1269,"rel":1270},"https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Fnecolas\u002Fnormalize.css\u002F",[31],"README"," 可以閱讀。",[16,1274,1275],{},"至今 Normalize.css 依然有在持續依據瀏覽器版本去更新，所以許多 CSS 框架都會以 Normalize.css 作為首選，例如：最知名的 Bootstrap 就是內建使用 Normalize.css。",[12,1277,1279],{"id":1278},"normalizecss-vs-reset-css","Normalize.css VS Reset CSS",[16,1281,1282],{},"最後應該會萌生一個想法，所以我實際上開發應該用 Reset CSS 還是 Normalize.css？",[16,1284,1285],{},"看完前面的分析之後，我們可以了解到 Reset CSS 的優缺點如下：",[16,1287,1288],{},"優點 - 所有預設樣式統一，盡可能統一所有樣式初始化\n缺點 - 每一個標籤都必須重新寫樣式，你也必須先知道有哪些標籤被清空了",[16,1290,1291],{},"Normalize.css 呢？",[16,1293,1294],{},"優點 - 保留預設樣式，減少重新撰寫樣式的美送。\n缺點 - 有非常低的機率發生樣式不統一，但這個機會已經很少了。",[16,1296,1297],{},"基本上我們可以知道 Normalize.css 與 Reset CSS 各有優缺點，但是你可能會想說 Normalize.css 感覺比較好，畢竟可以不用針對每一個標籤重新寫樣式，沒有錯，這確實是一個不爭的事實。",[16,1299,1300],{},"但實際上來講，其實我自己使用 Reset 機率依然是比較高的，因為往往設計師可能所要求的樣式會與原本 Normalize.css 所提供的預設樣式不同，那麼在這種情況之下其實選擇 Reset CSS 會比較乾脆直接，除非今天設計師就直接參考 Bootstrap 來製作畫面，那麼這種時候 Normalize.css 就會變成首選。",[16,1302,1303],{},"因此你說該選擇 Reset CSS 還是 Normalize.css 呢？不，這決定權在設計師身上。",[16,1305,1306],{},"但是這邊要注意如果你使用 Reset CSS 之後若搭配一些...例如 CKEditor、TinyMCE 這種網頁編輯器來開發的話，可能會發生標題、連結與項目列表都沒有樣式的囧事，所以在選擇 CSS 樣式時，請務必多加注意這一點。",[12,1308,1309],{"id":1309},"參考文獻",[348,1311,1312,1317,1322],{},[353,1313,1314],{},[27,1315,32],{"href":29,"rel":1316},[31],[353,1318,1319],{},[27,1320,1010],{"href":1030,"rel":1321},[31],[353,1323,1324],{},[27,1325,1328],{"href":1326,"rel":1327},"https:\u002F\u002Fstackoverflow.com\u002Fquestions\u002F6803250\u002Fcontent-vs-content-none\u002F6803278",[31],"content: '' vs content: none",[1330,1331,1332],"style",{},"html pre.shiki code .sQrFR, html code.shiki .sQrFR{--shiki-default:#BDC4CC}html pre.shiki code .sKpQp, html code.shiki .sKpQp{--shiki-default:#72F088}html pre.shiki code .sMAXC, html code.shiki .sMAXC{--shiki-default:#F0F3F6}html pre.shiki code .sCcAr, html code.shiki .sCcAr{--shiki-default:#91CBFF}html pre.shiki code .sWyjQ, html code.shiki .sWyjQ{--shiki-default:#FF9492}html pre.shiki code .sTRMh, html code.shiki .sTRMh{--shiki-default:#ADDCFF}html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}",{"title":55,"searchDepth":69,"depth":69,"links":1334},[1335,1336,1337,1342,1343],{"id":14,"depth":69,"text":14},{"id":21,"depth":69,"text":22},{"id":1009,"depth":69,"text":1010,"children":1338},[1339,1340,1341],{"id":1035,"depth":75,"text":1035},{"id":1170,"depth":75,"text":1021},{"id":1024,"depth":75,"text":1024},{"id":1278,"depth":69,"text":1279},{"id":1309,"depth":69,"text":1309},"CSS","2021-08-07 20:54:14","md","zh-Hant",{},"\u002Fcss\u002Freset-css-normalize-css","5",{"title":6,"description":18},false,"CSS\u002FReset-CSS-與-Normalize-css-差異",[1355,1010],"Reset CSS",null,"\u002Fcss\u002F20210807\u002F3641451940\u002F","I56wD_Lk06Tjv7uGijrWW-4BIhzJO-6hn13IHg_IaVM",{"newer":1360,"older":1364},{"url":1361,"title":1362,"date":1363},"\u002Fjavascript\u002F20210807\u002F3551792061\u002F","JavaScript 核心觀念(64) - ES6 章節：箭頭函式 - 箭頭函式簡介","2021-08-07 23:37:11",{"url":1365,"title":1366,"date":1367},"\u002Fjavascript\u002F20210801\u002F1905644146\u002F","JavaScript 核心觀念(63) - ES6 章節：Let 及 Const - Let 及 Const - 課後練習","2021-08-01 20:15:59",[1369,1373,1377],{"url":1370,"title":1371,"date":1372,"readingMinutes":1350},"\u002Fcss\u002F20260518\u002F2738592104\u002F","為什麼 CSS overflow: scroll 看不到捲軸？macOS 跟 Windows 的 Chrome 差異","2026-05-18 17:00:00",{"url":1374,"title":1375,"date":1376,"readingMinutes":1095},"\u002Fcss\u002F20240505\u002F2248376443\u002F","該如何避免使用者透過滑鼠選取特定元素？","2024-05-05 14:02:05",{"url":1378,"title":1379,"date":1380,"readingMinutes":1381},"\u002Fcss\u002F20210205\u002F1934188738\u002F","什麼！Bootstrap 4 變成 Bootstrap 5 了","2021-02-05 11:41:28","6",1784012764375]